"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The price of gas has gone up a lot in the UK and Europe after an attack on Qatar's Ras Laffan energy complex. This is not the first time Europe has faced problems related to energy.\",            \"english_title\": \"Gas Price Increase\",            \"translated_version\": \"El precio del gas ha subido mucho en el Reino Unido y Europa despu\u00e9s de un ataque al complejo de energ\u00eda Ras Laffan en Qatar. No es la primera vez que Europa tiene problemas con la energ\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Subida de Precio del Gas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The former head of counter-terrorism resigned on Tuesday because of the war with Iran. He said Iran does not pose an immediate threat to the US.\",            \"english_title\": \"Resignation Over Iran War\",            \"translated_version\": \"El exjefe de antiterrorismo renunci\u00f3 el martes por la guerra con Ir\u00e1n. Dijo que Ir\u00e1n no es una amenaza inmediata para Estados Unidos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Renuncia por Guerra con Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The actor has agreed to settle out of court with three men who accused him of sexual assault.\",            \"english_title\": \"Actor Settles Case\",            \"translated_version\": \"El actor acord\u00f3 resolver fuera de la corte con tres hombres que lo acusaron de abuso sexual.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Actor Resuelve Caso\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"News came out about an invitation after the monarch admitted there was a lot of abuse during the Spanish conquest of Mexico.\",            \"english_title\": \"Monarch's Admission\",            \"translated_version\": \"Salieron noticias sobre una invitaci\u00f3n despu\u00e9s de que el monarca admiti\u00f3 que hubo mucho abuso durante la conquista espa\u00f1ola de M\u00e9xico.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Admisi\u00f3n del Monarca\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The conflict between DR Congo and Rwanda continues even though they signed a peace deal in December.\",            \"english_title\": \"Conflict Continues\",            \"translated_version\": \"El conflicto entre la RD Congo y Ruanda contin\u00faa aunque firmaron un acuerdo de paz en diciembre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conflicto Contin\u00faa\"        }    ]}"